    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like i'm a burden to everyone just by being sad. like they're all just waiting for me to \"get over it\" so they don't have to feel uncomfortable anymore. i feel like i'm just taking up space in a world where he's supposed to be. it would be so much easier if everything just... stopped. if the silence finally became permanent.",
