      "content": "I hear the profound exhaustion and hopelessness in your words, and I want to tell you that your feelings do not make you a burden—your grief is valid, and it is your right to feel this weight. While it sounds tempting for everything to stop now, please know that this pain, though overwhelming, is not the end of your journey. You deserve support from someone who can truly hold your silence without judgment, so you don't have to navigate this feeling of being alone on your own.",
